values: Well just sitting here updating and changing my avatar on yahoo 360.  Hope I win.  Probably not, that's my luck.  well i'll let you all know soon.  i lost all my money the other week, just lost it.  don't know where it went.  if you find it can you send it back?  my feet are really cold right now.  stupid michigan.  why can't i live in cali like i want to?  oh yeah it's too damn expensive.

I'm getting more and more into this lj thing. work was pretty cool today, laid back and fun. cool people to work with. we even made toast and eggs for breakfast. yeah!! amanda you better write me on this lj soon or i'm personaly going to go to OK to kick your sorry booty!!!! isn't my icon the hottest ever. man he's the sexiest man around. sorry honey. haha.lol. adrian keeps getting into larry's dresser. and i've been on this computer like all day today and yesterday when i'm not working. ahhhh. i just wish i knew a little more about it and got more people to read my shit. anyway. later.

I just updated my yahoo 360 too.  Ellie has got the flu and is throwing up all over.  Yes, love that.  Can't wait for Lost to be new again and Prison Break to be back on again.  I watched 2Fast 2Furious the other day and the guy on that movie is the cell mate on Prison Break.  He's so funny. Anyway, we're thinking about moving into the basement so our daughter (3) can have her own room.  Any idea's on a smooth transfer for us and the kids?  I'm also trying to find some carpet pieces for the basement floor too.  Yeah good luck for that.

i cleaned my house like all day and then watched mean girls.  i want to go out tonight.  not going to happen though.  damn i had more freedom when i was 17 and 18 than i do now at 25.  kids kill any freedom you used to have.  right now adrian is crying because he fell off my bed (where he's not suppose to be anyway and i've told him like 3 times in the last 2 mins.) and ellie is coloring.  larry's on his way home from work and will probably find more shit to do today.  kendra is staying at home tonight bc she got wasted last night and doesn't want to drink.  i do, is that soooooo bad.  darn it.  i'm so damn bored.  get me out of here!!!!!!!!!  christmas party for work is next friday.  can't wait, get to dress up and hang out with kendra.  larry has to work of course. so i don't want to go by myself so i asked kendra.  later!!!

Everyone in my family is sick.  But I'm the only one without a fever.  Larry even called in to work yesterday.  And we all know how he is with his job and shit.  Mom and Dad put the house on the market and they've already got a purchase aggement.  Cool.  They'll be out of here and happier soon.  Work is alright.  I applied for a job in Alma yesterday.  We'll see how that goes.  I don't know it's a third shift job so I don't know if I really want it.

Just sitting here again.  Not doing anything really.  I'm sick, got a chest cold.  And of course Larry's been outside all day and now he might go bowling.  Oh and he went to get his truck.  So much for a mom who needs a little rest and relaxation.  Not going to happen here when Larry could give a rat's ass if I feel better.  As long as everyone else is happy including himself and excluding me.  Then everything is great.  Later.

Why do men think they can do whatever they want and their women will just sit by and watch them do it?  I have to admit sometimes I am that kind of woman, but I'm getting really sick and tired of it.  Shit.  I'm sick of either laying down and letting him get his way or get titled a bitch if I don't.  Man it makes me so mad.

just sitting here being bored as usual.  larry and steve are outside working on steve's car, like usual.  and the kids are sleeping.  we went and got pumkins today.  so i guess i'm going to have to get them carved up here pretty soon.  my life is pretty boring.  i want to sleep but i don't.  and after this i'm going to look on ebay and see if i can start to sell anything, like scrapbook pages and stuff.  later.

Why do I always think I have to put something for the subject line?  I don't know, I don't like the subject line.  Also other things I don't like....

   When people cut you off on the road!
   When people scrape their teeth across their silverwear,  ahhh!
   People who steal, if you have my cd's or larry's speaker and amp, give it back!
   People who are consistantly late!
   People who say they'll do something and then bitch out last minute!
   People who feel better about themselves when they cut other people down!
   People who beat, neglect or in any way abuse child, mentally disabled or elderly people, especially children, what can a child do to defend themselves.  Bastards.  Sorry get a little passionate about that.
   Bitches for no reason.
   People who complain all the time (I'm one of those though, opps.)

Alright, enough soapboxing.  Whatever.  Watching the Red Wings, love them!!  Draper just got taken to the hospital.  I bet someone gets revenge for him and Homer.  Alright later so I can finish watching them.  Later.

Well Larry, Kendra and Steve all went bowling and left me behind.  I worked my butt off to find two babysitters for tomorrow to go up north and then they want ME to find another one for tonight.  I don't think so.  Amy if you read this know that I didn't want to call you or your sisters to babysit tonight.  I thought it was rude to ask you guys to do so so late and on a weekend and Annie is already babysitting Eathan tomorrow.  I couldn't ask you and I didn't know Steve tried to call you guys until after he already did.  Sorry.  Well I hope they're having fun.  I'm always left behind.  Larry would rather have fun than show his loyality to me.  Steve didn't go last time because they couldn't find a babysitter and Kendra had to stay home.  Larry couldn't do that to me.  I don't know why I have no control over Larry.  Anyway.  Check out my yahoo 360 website too!.  Later.

Well it seems like all I do is clean and work.  Larry was suppose to let me sleep in today but that's a lie.  I'm the one up and he's still sleeping.  Figures.  He got up to feed the kids, but only after I had to tell him like 20 times.  Crapsucker.  Well anyway I'm hungry and want breakfast that he promised to make me.  Should have known that wouldn't have happened.  Oh well got a job interview on Tuesday, but I think I have to travel.  Can't do that.  I'll let you know how it goes.  Later.

I need some feedback here.  Just want to see if anyone out there is even reading this shit I write.  About to watch that new amazing race.  what does everyone think about it.  let me know.
Well no one told me any secrets.  All shy people I guess.  I got some new icons of Lost from random searches.  Okay I'm leaving, I'm hungry and Larry is snoring.

I saw this on another site.  Tell me your secret.  Tell me something about yourself that no one knows, the one thing you keep to yourself.  Leave it anonamous or whatever.  See what everyone else has to say about themselves.  It's fun and therapetic.  Have fun!

Well some bad news this weekend.  My cousin Devin was killed in a car accident this Wednesday.  He was 18 years young and a very good boy.  I loved him so much.  And he loved life so much too.  But the Lord had other plans for Devin and I'm gratefull for the years we had with him.  Devin, I'll see you later when I come and join you and Grandma.  Take care of her and watch over your parents.  They love you and miss you so much!  God Bless.  Miss you!
